comments: Paul (OKC) makes marginal contact with Covington (HOU) during his shot attempt.
Paul (OKC) and Covington (HOU) briefly engage and separate during the rebound.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) makes marginal contact with Gordon (HOU) while setting the screen.
Westbrook (HOU) makes marginal contact with Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) at the start of the drive.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) releases the pass prior to his foot landing on the ground.
Adams (OKC) is in the lane for longer than three seconds.
Tucker (HOU) makes contact to the ball with his foot, but does not intentionally kick it.
Adams (OKC) and Tucker (HOU) briefly engage and separate during the rebound.
Gordon (HOU) goes to not through Paul (OKC). Paul's reaction is not consistent with the level of contact.
Adams (OKC) maintains a legal guarding position on Gordon (HOU) and cleanly steals the ball.
Paul (OKC) goes to not through Harden (HOU) during his drive. Harden's reaction is not consistent with the level of contact.
Tucker (HOU) and Dort (OKC) engage and disengage during the rebound.
Dort (OKC) maintains a legal guarding position on Harden (HOU) during the drive.
Tucker (HOU) establishes his position in Schroder's (OKC) path while setting the screen and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Schroder (OKC) rests his hand on Westbrook's (HOU) body and makes marginal contact as he moves along his path to defend the shot attempt.
Covington (HOU) maintains a legal guarding position on Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC).
Harden (HOU) cleanly blocks Dort's (OKC) shot attempt, jumping to his side and making clean contact with the ball.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Referees conduct a replay review following the ball going out of bounds and determine that Dort (OKC) jumped from out of bounds and made contact with the ball, and 1.4 seconds is added to the game clock.
Dort (OKC) and Harden (HOU) briefly engage and separate during the inbound.
Dort (OKC) commits a take foul on Harden (HOU).
Dort (OKC) commits a take foul on Covington (HOU).

Before the inbound, Harden (HOU) holds Paul (OKC) and an away from the play foul is called.  During the inbound, Coach Donovan (OKC) attempts to call a timeout but the foul occurs prior to the timeout.
Adams (OKC) and Tucker (HOU) engage and disengage during the rebound.
Westbrook (OKC) deflects the pass away before making incidental contact with Adams (OKC).
